metadata.name: Golden moments
metadata.description:
Golden moments - an edition piece by Bogdan Ianosi

Being a summer child, I love the warmth and vibrance of the summer days. Slow days at the seaside are the times when I recharge and fill myself with positive energy. 

This edition celebrates those times which I call ‘golden moments’ and represents the best how I feel about summer.

This photograph was taken in Rovinj, Croatia in the summer of 2021 and it was shot on 35mm Kodak film.

attributes.value: Leica M6 & Voigtlander 35mm 1.4 lens - Kodak Gold 200
